                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Security Council</ENAMEX>. The creation of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NCTC</ENAMEX> should help the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NSC</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">staff</ENAMEX> concentrate on
