                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">intelligence</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">entities</ENAMEX> in this program is then presented to the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">president</ENAMEX> and
                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Congress</ENAMEX> in <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">15</NUMEX> separate volumes.
