                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">committees</ENAMEX>. Those <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">committees</ENAMEX> have no <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">subcommittees</ENAMEX> just for intelligence, and only a
