            The appropriations for the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CIA</ENAMEX> and the national intelligence <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">agencies</ENAMEX>- <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NSA</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NGA</ENAMEX>, and
                NRO-are then given to the secretary of defense. The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">secretary</ENAMEX> transfers the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CIA</ENAMEX>'s
