            In addition, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DCI</ENAMEX> lacks hire-and-fire authority over most of the intelligence
                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">community</ENAMEX>'s senior <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">managers</ENAMEX>. For the national intelligence <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">agencies</ENAMEX> housed in the
                <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Defense Department</ENAMEX>, the secretary of defense must seek the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">DCI</ENAMEX>'s concurrence
